  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Stack towering sandwiches with the help of cute cat friends while building up your dream cat cafe. With plenty of hungry quirky customers around, you’ll need to upgrade your cafe, find new cats to help you and up your sandwich game to keep them happy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy 2 to 3 hours of arcade style gameplay where you can use the money you make selling delicious sandwiches to buy new ingredients, new customization options and, of course, fun toys and other items for your cat friends! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/12c34b2bd0a94437137b1ee003f20cb3.poster.avif?t=1765972851\" width=616 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/12c34b2bd0a94437137b1ee003f20cb3.webm?t=1765972851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/12c34b2bd0a94437137b1ee003f20cb3.mp4?t=1765972851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >It’s a Cat Cafe after all</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We, cat lovers, all know that each kitty is unique so each one you befriend will add something special to your cafe. Anything from keeping customers happy to helping you make delicious sandwiches!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/a524918d66b91f98ea85bb462e090b38.poster.avif?t=1765972851\" width=616 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/a524918d66b91f98ea85bb462e090b38.webm?t=1765972851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/a524918d66b91f98ea85bb462e090b38.mp4?t=1765972851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Up your sandwich game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By upgrading your cafe you’ll be able to add new ingredients to the menu, unlock exciting new combinations and add fun new interactions! Enjoy discovering various unlockables throughout your cat cafe journey! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/6cc8de940983abc6f3a5053f29bbb2b6.poster.avif?t=1765972851\" width=616 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/6cc8de940983abc6f3a5053f29bbb2b6.webm?t=1765972851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/6cc8de940983abc6f3a5053f29bbb2b6.mp4?t=1765972851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hats, Decorations & More</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to upgrades you can spend your earnings on new beautiful decorations for your cafe as well as cute accessories for your team of kitties! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/04524c49700b2b7e0cdace10497dd778.webp?t=1765972851\" width=616 height=41 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The more you know</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many cats in our game are based on real pets from our lives! 😻 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Similarly, many customers are modeled after our amazing friends and family! ❤ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/a27a661fec87c85c9521a6fae0bf6d08.avif?t=1765972851\" width=201 height=138 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Stack towering sandwiches with the help of cute cat friends while building up your dream cat cafe. With plenty of hungry quirky customers around, you’ll need to upgrade your cafe, find new cats to help you and up your sandwich game to keep them happy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy 2 to 3 hours of arcade style gameplay where you can use the money you make selling delicious sandwiches to buy new ingredients, new customization options and, of course, fun toys and other items for your cat friends! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/12c34b2bd0a94437137b1ee003f20cb3.poster.avif?t=1765972851\" width=616 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/12c34b2bd0a94437137b1ee003f20cb3.webm?t=1765972851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/12c34b2bd0a94437137b1ee003f20cb3.mp4?t=1765972851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >It’s a Cat Cafe after all</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We, cat lovers, all know that each kitty is unique so each one you befriend will add something special to your cafe. Anything from keeping customers happy to helping you make delicious sandwiches!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/a524918d66b91f98ea85bb462e090b38.poster.avif?t=1765972851\" width=616 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/a524918d66b91f98ea85bb462e090b38.webm?t=1765972851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/a524918d66b91f98ea85bb462e090b38.mp4?t=1765972851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Up your sandwich game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By upgrading your cafe you’ll be able to add new ingredients to the menu, unlock exciting new combinations and add fun new interactions! Enjoy discovering various unlockables throughout your cat cafe journey! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/6cc8de940983abc6f3a5053f29bbb2b6.poster.avif?t=1765972851\" width=616 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/6cc8de940983abc6f3a5053f29bbb2b6.webm?t=1765972851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/6cc8de940983abc6f3a5053f29bbb2b6.mp4?t=1765972851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hats, Decorations & More</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to upgrades you can spend your earnings on new beautiful decorations for your cafe as well as cute accessories for your team of kitties! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/04524c49700b2b7e0cdace10497dd778.webp?t=1765972851\" width=616 height=41 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The more you know</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many cats in our game are based on real pets from our lives! 😻 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Similarly, many customers are modeled after our amazing friends and family! ❤ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658690/extras/a27a661fec87c85c9521a6fae0bf6d08.avif?t=1765972851\" width=201 height=138 /></span></p>",
